### 2. Flight Deals Tracker
- Uses external APIs and Sheety.
- Tracks flight prices and updates data dynamically.
- Sends alerts when flight prices drop.

### 3. Rain Alert App
- Uses weather API to check rain forecast.
- Sends SMS/notification if rain is expected.

